Class TransactionSummaryVO

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.strohalm.cyclos.utils.DataObject

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class TransactionSummaryVO
extends DataObject
    Contais report data of invoice or transaction amounts. Just keeps two kinds of numbers for any transaction amounts: the total sum of amounts, and a counter representing the number of amounts added.
